## M15b.1: unbound call must be a Rig diagnostic, not silent unknown.
##
## Per GPT-5.5 entry 39 + post-impl review: "`unknown` may only
## exist as poison after a diagnostic, never as a silent success
## type." Pre-M15b.1, this file exited 0 from `bin/rig check`
## and only Zig caught the missing identifier with a confusing
## `error: use of undeclared identifier 'nonexistent_fn'`.

sub main()
  print(nonexistent_fn())
